<p>How I can make ckEditor pasted text without br-tags? For example, i writing in notepad:</p>  <pre><code>text1 text2 text3 </code></pre>  <p>and ckEditor pasted this with this code:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;p&gt;     text1&lt;br/&gt;     text2&lt;br/&gt;     text3&lt;br/&gt; &lt;/p&gt; </code></pre>  <p>But I need to get:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;p&gt;text1&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;text2&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;text3&lt;/p&gt; </code></pre>